    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294300/extras/d10f277d595b1759448b26d6171af42f.avif?t=1770237648\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294300/extras_big/d10f277d595b1759448b26d6171af42f.avif?t=1770237648 width=800 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own island with the special editor! You have no limits or restrictions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294300/extras/1cd00f9b2e3ece355fec85468bbede9a.avif?t=1770237648\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294300/extras_big/1cd00f9b2e3ece355fec85468bbede9a.avif?t=1770237648 width=800 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Populate the island with dinosaurs. You have more than 50 dinosaur species to choose from. Do you want herbivores, predators or pterosaurs?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294300/extras/9bfd40d40b79187da8d41e7b77c4b244.avif?t=1770237648\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294300/extras_big/9bfd40d40b79187da8d41e7b77c4b244.avif?t=1770237648 width=800 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each dinosaur has specific needs. Ensure the mutual symbiosis and prosperity of all species on the island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294300/extras/5637a3c1afa9db54991b44eb273b32d5.avif?t=1770237648\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294300/extras_big/5637a3c1afa9db54991b44eb273b32d5.avif?t=1770237648 width=800 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If necessary, you can personally control any dinosaur.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
